high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees and walk towards the stove, turning left 90 degrees when you reach it.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk towards the sink.
Slice the apple in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Take an apple slice out of the sink.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk towards the stove, turning to the right 90 degrees when you reach it.
Put the apple slice in the cupboard above the stove.
Take the plate out of the cupboard with the apple slice.
Turn around 180 degrees and cross the room, turning to the left 90 degrees when you reach the fridge and open it.
Place the plate inside the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with an apple slice on it into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right walk forward then turn left on the counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn around to your left face the sink
Slice the apple in the sink
Put the knife in the sink
Pick up the slice apple in the sink
Turn left then face the cabinet above the stove
Open the cabinet put the slice apple on the plate
Pick up the plate with apple
Turn to your right the walk straight go to the fridge
Open the fridge and put in the plate with apple

high_descs: Walk to the counter
Pick up knife from the counter
Turn to the sink
Cut the apple in the sink to three pieces
Put the knife in the sink

Walk to the top shelf
Open the shelf and put the apple piece on the plate in the shelf
Take the plate out of the shelf
